{
  "title": {
    "en": "Set what a smart task may do"
  },
  "titleFormatted": {
    "en": "Allow [[device]]'s smart task to [[property]] [[when]]"
  },
  "hint": {
    "en": "Choose what PELS may do to keep this smart task's deadline, and when — go over today's budget, or limit lower-priority devices so this task gets the power it needs. 'While it's scheduled to run' applies it the whole time the task is active; the change takes effect on the next plan refresh and sticks until you change it or clear the smart task."
